OL,3,CGovernment must apologise for historic
OL,4,Cforced adoption, MPs say
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Social Affairs
OL,7,FCorrespondent Sarah Corker & Senior
OL,8,FProducer Lottie Kilraine
OL,10,FThe government must issue a formal,
OL,11,Funqualified apology to survivors of
OL,12,Fforced adoption who have "suffered for
OL,13,Ftoo long", a cross-party committee of
OL,14,FMPs has said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
