FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774725064
OL,3,CGovernment must apologise for historic
OL,4,Cforced adoption, MPs say
OL,6,FIn post-war Britain an estimated
OL,7,F250,000 unmarried women were sent to
OL,8,Finstitutions run by religious
OL,9,Forganisations and the state, where
OL,10,Fthey were pressured and coerced to put
OL,11,Ftheir babies up for adoption between
OL,12,Fthe 1940s and 1980s. Other infants
OL,13,Fdied through poor care.
OL,15,FThe practice caused "unimaginable
OL,16,Ftrauma" for generations of women and
OL,17,Fleft "profound, often devastating
OL,18,Fimpacts" on their children, the Chair
OL,19,Fof the Education Committee, Helen
OL,20,FHayes, said on Friday.
OL,26,@xD@GO]yD@FOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774725064
OL,3,CGovernment must apologise for historic
OL,4,Cforced adoption, MPs say
OL,6,FThe committee has called for the
OL,7,Fgovernment to commit to an apology for
OL,8,Fthe state's role in the scandal, with
OL,9,FMPs saying the matter must be treated
OL,10,Fwith urgency "given the advancing age
OL,11,Fof those affected".
OL,13,FThe damning report comes after an
OL,14,Fongoing ITV News investigation has
OL,15,Flaid bare the trauma and neglect faced
OL,16,Fby both mothers and their children,
OL,17,Fnow adults, many of whom are still
OL,18,Fsearching for answers or have since
OL,19,Fdied.
OL,26,@rD@NOUsD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/21
