OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774725064
OL,3,CGovernment must apologise for historic
OL,4,Cforced adoption, MPs say
OL,6,FAnn Keen, a former Labour MP and
OL,7,Fnurse, whose only child was taken from
OL,8,Fher in 1966 recalled having "no
OL,9,Fdignity" or say over what happened to
OL,10,Fher at a mother and baby institution
OL,11,Fin Swansea.
OL,13,FWhen asked by MPs why an apology
OL,14,Fmatters, Ms Keen said "it would mean
OL,15,Fthe world" to her because "I still
OL,16,Fblame myself".
OL,26,@vD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/21
