OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774725064
OL,3,CGovernment must apologise for historic
OL,4,Cforced adoption, MPs say
OL,6,F"I want this apology to clear not only
OL,7,Fmy name, but that of my son, because I
OL,8,Fdid not give him away," she added. "My
OL,9,Fson did not know he was adopted until
OL,10,Fhe was 27 years old."
OL,12,FAdult adoptees have described being
OL,13,Fseen as a "solution" for their
OL,14,Fadoptive parents.
OL,16,FIt took Debbie Iromlou, who is a
OL,17,Ftransracial adoptee, nearly 40 years
OL,18,Fto trace her birth family - a journey
OL,19,Fwhich took her halfway across the
OL,20,Fworld.
OL,26,@rD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
