CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774725064
OL,3,CGovernment must apologise for historic
OL,4,Cforced adoption, MPs say
OL,6,FGrowing up in Suffolk in the 1960s and
OL,7,F1970s, she had no idea that the mother
OL,8,Fraising her was not her biological
OL,9,Fmother.
OL,11,FIt was only when Debbie turned 16 and
OL,12,Fher foster mother had made a request
OL,13,Fto formally adopt her that the truth
OL,14,Fcame out.
OL,16,FDebbie Iromlou, who gave evidence to
OL,17,FMPs earlier this month, spoke to ITV
OL,18,FNews last year about her childhood and
OL,19,Fadoption
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
