FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774725064
OL,3,CGovernment must apologise for historic
OL,4,Cforced adoption, MPs say
OL,6,F"There was no safeguarding," she told
OL,7,FMPs. "Nobody came to check on us, and
OL,8,Fneglect and abuse in adoptive families
OL,9,Fwas common.
OL,11,F"Local authorities had warned them
OL,12,Fthat my foster mother - soon to be
OL,13,Fadoptive mother - was not fit to take
OL,14,Fchildren in. They ignored those
OL,15,Frecommendations, and I was left there
OL,16,Fanyway."
OL,18,FGiving evidence to the committee, Dr
OL,19,FMichael Lambert of Lancaster
OL,20,FUniversity said that "coercion was
OL,21,Fbaked into the entire system".
OL,26,@xD@HO]|D@VOU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/21
