OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774725064
OL,3,CGovernment must apologise for historic
OL,4,Cforced adoption, MPs say
OL,6,FHe characterised the system as one
OL,7,F"designed to supply infants to
OL,8,Fadoptive families", rather than to
OL,9,Fsupport mothers in making a genuine
OL,10,Fdecision about the future of their
OL,11,Fbaby.
OL,13,FSuccessive governments have previously
OL,14,Fsaid the state wasn't directly
OL,15,Finvolved in these practices but ITV
OL,16,FNews has seen evidence in official
OL,17,Ffiles that they were funding, through
OL,18,Flocal health authority grants, 171
OL,19,Fhomes across England.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@RO]
