OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774725064
OL,3,CGovernment must apologise for historic
OL,4,Cforced adoption, MPs say
OL,6,FITV News' years-long investigation
OL,7,Finto the forced adoption scandal has
OL,8,Falready revealed hundreds of unmarked
OL,9,Fgraves of babies born in state and
OL,10,Fchurch-run homes across England, with
OL,11,Fallegations that sick or premature
OL,12,Fchildren were left to die as they
OL,13,Fweren't deemed "desirable" for
OL,14,Fadoption.
OL,16,FLast year, we revealed nearly 200
OL,17,Finfants who died at eight mother and
OL,18,Fbaby homes are buried in mass plots in
OL,19,Ften different cemeteries across
OL,20,FEngland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774725064
OL,3,CGovernment must apologise for historic
OL,4,Cforced adoption, MPs say
OL,6,FTo this day, families are still
OL,7,Fsearching for their lost children
OL,8,Fconnected to these post-war
OL,9,Finstitutions.
OL,11,FA formal apology is essential in order
OL,12,Fto correct the public record, address
OL,13,Fprevious misrepresentations and reduce
OL,14,Fthe burdens felt by many mothers and
OL,15,Fadoptees, the committee found.
OL,17,FIt has urged the government to work
OL,18,F"as quickly as possible" and commit
OL,19,Fpublicly to a clear timetable for
OL,20,Fdeveloping and issuing its apology.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
