OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774725064
OL,3,CGovernment must apologise for historic
OL,4,Cforced adoption, MPs say
OL,6,F'We want the apology to lead to
OL,7,Fmeaningful action for survivors,'
OL,8,FHelen Hayes, the Chair of the
OL,9,FEducation Committee, told ITV News
OL,11,FEarlier this month, children and
OL,12,Ffamilies minister Josh MacAlister
OL,13,Fconfirmed an apology for the state's
OL,14,Frole in historical forced adoption was
OL,15,Fbeing "actively considered" by the
OL,16,Fgovernment.
OL,26,@wD@GOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
