OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774725064
OL,3,CGovernment must apologise for historic
OL,4,Cforced adoption, MPs say
OL,6,FThe Education Committee's report said
OL,7,Fan apology should cover a wider period
OL,8,F"as we have received clear evidence
OL,9,Fthat the practices associated with
OL,10,Fforced adoptions happened before 1949
OL,11,Fand continued after the introduction
OL,12,Fof the Adoption Act 1976".
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/21
