OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774725064
OL,3,CGovernment must apologise for historic
OL,4,Cforced adoption, MPs say
OL,6,FOther countries where forced adoption
OL,7,Ftook place, including Canada,
OL,8,FAustralia, Republic of Ireland,
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland, Scotland and Wales,
OL,10,Fhave already issued a formal
OL,11,Fgovernment apology, and in some cases
OL,12,Fset up redress schemes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
