OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774725064
OL,3,CGovernment must apologise for historic
OL,4,Cforced adoption, MPs say
OL,6,FIn August 2025, former Labour Prime
OL,7,FMinster Gordon Brown, whose time in
OL,8,Foffice led to similar high-profile
OL,9,Fapologies, added his voice to the
OL,10,Fcampaign for an official apology
OL,11,Ftelling ITV News that the state must
OL,12,Facknowledge "the damage that was done"
OL,13,Fand its role in this "terrible
OL,14,Ftragedy".
OL,16,FThe committee chair said a formal
OL,17,Fapology is an "essential step" towards
OL,18,F"delivering the peace survivors
OL,19,Fdeserve".
OL,26,@{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
