CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774725064
OL,3,CGovernment must apologise for historic
OL,4,Cforced adoption, MPs say
OL,6,F"Survivors have suffered for far too
OL,7,Flong," Ms Hayes added. "They simply
OL,8,Fwant to move on with their lives."
OL,10,FIf you want to share your experience
OL,11,Fwith ITV News, get in touch by
OL,12,Femailing: socialaffairs@itv.com
OL,14,FHowever, the review stopped short of
OL,15,Frecommending financial redress for
OL,16,Fsurvivors.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@XOU
