OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774725064
OL,3,CGovernment must apologise for historic
OL,4,Cforced adoption, MPs say
OL,6,FIt did call on the government to carry
OL,7,Fout a "rigorous assessment" of how
OL,8,Fother governments around the world had
OL,9,Fhandled the issue "with special
OL,10,Fattention to the redress mechanisms
OL,11,Fintroduced in Australia, Northern
OL,12,FIreland and the Republic of Ireland".
OL,14,FMPs have also called for improved
OL,15,Faccess to records for adoptees and
OL,16,Fmothers, and access to traumainformed
OL,17,Fsupport for those navigating contact
OL,18,Fand reunion with their families.
OL,26,@oD@GOUoD@[O]qD@SOUtD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/21
