OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774725064
OL,3,CGovernment must apologise for historic
OL,4,Cforced adoption, MPs say
OL,6,FThere needs to be a clear legal duty
OL,7,Fon record-holding institutions to
OL,8,Fmaintain and securely store their
OL,9,Frecords, and new guidance to local
OL,10,Fauthorities to improve those seeking
OL,11,Finformation about their records, MPs
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
